 the Gaia team's\nparallax spatial covariance model to brighter magnitudes ($G < 13$) and smaller\nscales (down to $\\approx 0.1\\deg$), where systematic EDR3 parallax\nuncertainties are at least $\\approx 3-4 \\mu \\mathrm{as}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2021 18:59:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Mar 2021 17:39:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 20:14:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
