2\\pm0.026$. For Cyg OB2-12 we predict $p(10\\mu{\\rm\nm})=(2.1\\pm0.3)\\%$, which should be observable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2021 19:00:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
